body_html:
Thanks @freedomtan

Just to be extra clear, the proper size is 224, not 244. And you can also run the benchmark tool without specifying those parameters:

$ bazel run //tensorflow/contrib/lite/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model -- \
    --graph=`realpath ~/Downloads/mobilenet_v2*.tflite`
...
Average inference timings in us: Warmup: 46891, Init: 5050, no stats: 33320.6
...

body:
Thanks @freedomtan 

Just to be extra clear, the proper size is 224, not 244. And you can also run the benchmark tool without specifying those parameters:

```
$ bazel run //tensorflow/contrib/lite/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model -- \
    --graph=`realpath ~/Downloads/mobilenet_v2*.tflite`
...
Average inference timings in us: Warmup: 46891, Init: 5050, no stats: 33320.6
...
```
